 37→  test: "Execute structured browser-based testing for GitHub issue #{issue}. Run the /test {issue} workflow.",
 38→  qa: "Review the implementation for GitHub issue #{issue} against acceptance criteria. Run the /qa {issue} workflow.",
 39→  loop: "Parse test/QA findings for GitHub issue #{issue} and iterate until quality gates pass. Run the /loop {issue} workflow.",
