 47→
 48→/**
 49→ * Cold-start retry threshold in seconds.
 50→ * Failures under this duration are likely Claude Code subprocess initialization
 51→ * issues rather than genuine phase failures (based on empirical data: cold-start
 52→ * failures consistently complete in 15-39s vs 150-310s for real work).
 53→ */
 54→const COLD_START_THRESHOLD_SECONDS = 60;
 55→const COLD_START_MAX_RETRIES = 2;
